text: Rimantė Jonušaitė (born 25 October 2003) is a Lithuanian footballer who plays as a forward and has appeared for the Lithuania women's national team. ==Career== Jonušaitė has been capped for the Lithuania national team, appearing for the team during the UEFA Women's Euro 2021 qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:2003 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football forwards Category:Lithuanian women's footballers Category:Lithuania women's international footballers Category:Gintra Universitetas players
